DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260317T200000
SUMMARY:Splat Space Community Biolab meeting
DESCRIPTION:Splat Space - Durham's Hackerspace\nWe will meet to discuss in
 dividual or group research projects\, logistics of our bio space at SplatS
 pace\, or developments in biology. Attendees are encouraged to lead a disc
 ussion on any of these topics. Non-Splat members are welcome.
