DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260328T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260328T130000
SUMMARY:Monthly Cleanup
DESCRIPTION:Splat Space - Durham's Hackerspace\nThe last Saturday of each 
 month is our Cleanup Day. It's a chance for our members to come together t
 o help make Splat Space more organized. Whether it's sorting bolts\, vacuu
 ming the carpets\, removing scrap or re-arranging the space\, anything tha
 t helps to make the space more open and organized is appreciated.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/splatspace/events/313696051/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260308T163317Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260308T163317Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
